Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a cruel angel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become a legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When a blue wind{\i0}\N{\i1}Knocks on the door to your heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just gaze back at me{\i0}\N{\i1}And smile oh so gently{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So eager for something{\i0}\N{\i1}You touch so softly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those innocent eyes{\i0}\N{\i1}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But one day, you will realize{\i0}\N{\i1}That upon your back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have wings{\i0}\N{\i1}You can fly to the faraway future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cruel angel's thesis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, you'll take off through a window{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your overflowing pathos{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leads you to betray your memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become legend, young boy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}RAISON D'ÊTRE{\i0},{\i1\i0}ONE'S REASON FOR BEING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,THE REASON IT'S OKAY TO BE HERE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CASE OF SHINJI IKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A BOY WISHED FOR HIS OWN DEATH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A BOY GRANTED HIS WISH
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,THE FINAL ANGEL IS GONE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,YET SHINJI IKARI AGONIZES OVER IT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY DID YOU KILL HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY DID YOU KILL HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:01:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY DID YOU KILL HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY DID YOU KILL HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY DID YOU KILL HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY DID YOU KILL HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Kaworu was... He was an Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,WASN'T HE AS HUMAN AS YOU ARE?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He was an Angel! Our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,WASN'T HE AS HUMAN AS YOU ARE?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! He wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was a person just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No! He was an Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! If I hadn't,\Nwe all would have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone would have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to do it!\NBut there was no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,SO YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,SO YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,SO YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,SO YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,SO YOU KILLED HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you! Somebody, please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if only one of us could survive,\Nit should have been him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a way better person than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaworu should have survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. Only those with\Nthe will to live get to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He craved death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He abandoned his will to live\Nand clung to a false hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't do anything wrong, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really do the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.13,0:03:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Being rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,By who? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid... of Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was abandoned by Father. He hated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What will I do if people hate me?\NWhat should I do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see anything.\NI can't make anything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where did you go, Ms. Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where should I go from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato! Asuka! Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohji! Kensuke! Ms. Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me what I should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, is piloting this all I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to pilot this again\Nlike Father and everybody else says?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means killing people I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Say something! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY DO YOU PILOT THE EVA?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people tell me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT'S WHY YOU PILOT THE EVA?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To... To help everyone!\NWhat's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU PILOT THE EVA TO HELP EVERYONE?\NTO HELP OTHERS?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! That's a great thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a really great thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody praises me when I do!\NEverybody takes care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, an idiot? That means\Nyou're actually doing it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again, making excuses\Nto yourself right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The mindset that you're\Ndoing your best to serve others,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a cop-out right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What it boils down to\Nis that you're lonely, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just dependency!\NA symbiotic relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just hoping that\Nyou'll be needed by others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just sitting around, waiting for\Nsomeone to bring happiness to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To bring you {\i1}false{\i0} happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you do the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,OUR SECOND CHARACTER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CASE OF ASUKA LANGLEY SORYU
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember getting in,\Nbut I'm back in the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Forced back into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like this busted\Npiece of junk even works.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I guess {\i1}I'm{\i0}\Nthe busted piece of junk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't want me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody would ever want me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody needs a pilot\Nwho can't operate an Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking to others\Nto define yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,SEPARATION ANXIETY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of being alone, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid that if everyone else\Ngoes away, so will you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you pilot your Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that crap,\Nnot from a doll like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OUR THIRD CHARACTER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CASE OF REI AYANAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But who... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,REI AYANAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're also Rei Ayanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm an object\Nthat's called Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all objects that\Nare called Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are all of you me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because other people\Nall call us Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have a heart and body\Nthat are forgeries?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't forgeries. Because I'm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're a person whose fake soul
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,was created by a human named Gendoh Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a fake object\Nthat is pretending to be a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See that? Inside of you is a heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a dark, impenetrable,\Nunfathomable abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}real{\i0} you is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I became myself\Nover the time that I've existed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and through the connections\Nthat I've formed with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The person I am is shaped by\Nmy interactions with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Interactions with others\Nand the passage of time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,will change the shape of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,THOSE ARE LINKS?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Those are what created\Nthe person that I have been,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the object called Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They will create the person I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,THOSE ARE LINKS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's another, {\i1}real{\i0} you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to see her, so you just\Nkeep avoiding her subconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE YOU'RE AFRAID
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she might not be human in shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the person you have been\Nup until now might disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE AFRAID
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid that who you are\Nwill vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid that you'll disappear\Nfrom everyone's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid? Why would I be afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own personal world\Nwould disappear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,ISN'T THAT SCARY?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you would disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ISN'T THAT SCARY?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that would make me happy.\NI want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want is despair.\NI want to return to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't.\NI can't return to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't let me go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't let me go, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I came into existence because he needs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's over now.\NI won't be needed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be abandoned by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had always longed for that day,\Nbut now I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you were born for, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,AND...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,THE INSTRUMENTALITY OF HUMANITY BEGINS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,BACK TO SHINJI IKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've felt it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the lines of my body\Nare melting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm getting bigger,\Nspreading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever... and ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS WAS HOW EVERYONE'S\NINSTRUMENTALITY BEGAN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,PARTS THEY WERE MISSING
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,HEARTS THEY HAD LOST
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT EMPTINESS IN THEIR HEARTS WAS FILLED
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE INSTRUMENTALITY OF\NTHE HEART, THE SOUL, BEGINS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,EVERYONE'S INSTRUMENTALITY BEGINS,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,RETURNING EVERYTHING TO NOTHINGNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we aren't returning to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm simply returning everything\Nto its beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning to the mother\Nwho has been lost to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hearts will become one,\Nand we will achieve eternal peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all this is, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Instrumentality Project?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We all have a part of our heart\Nthat is forever empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Something we have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS CAUSES EMOTIONAL STARVATION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS CAUSES EMOTIONAL ANXIETY AND FEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We all fear that darkness within us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and we live our lives\Ntrying to escape it or banish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there are people,\Nthat darkness will never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think we should merge\Neveryone's hearts together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to get them to make each other whole?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And without anyone's consent?!\NWhat gives you the right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just forcing people\Nto cozy up to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you yourself\Nalways wanted the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CASE OF MISATO KATSURAGI\N(PART 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my heart inside\Nyour heart, Ms. Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the same, it's also my heart\Ninside your heart, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For me to find myself, I need to interact\Nwith lots of different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to take a good look inside myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to take a good look at\Nthe Ms. Misato that's inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Misato, what do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,DO YOU WANT TO BE A GOOD GIRL?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Daddy is always gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:12:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to be a good girl and help Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to end up like Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Mommy is always crying\Nwhen Daddy is away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't cry. I shouldn't act spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need to be a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll make sure that\NDaddy won't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate my father.\NThat's why I hate being a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it... I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tired of keeping myself\Nall clean and pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tired of the me that keeps up\Nthe charade of being clean and pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get sullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see myself absolutely filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you slept with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I loved him.\NThat's why I slept with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you really in love with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.\NHe accepted me for who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU SURE?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He was gentle with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please! Don't show that to Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to get\Nembarrassed about at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were fine with it\Nin front of the man you loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you {\i1}loved{\i0}\Nparading around off like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, you actually love\Nletting Shinji see you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie! You're wrong! Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really your father\Nthat you want to show this to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to find solace\Nin Ryoji's face as he slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to find solace\Nin the warmth of Ryoji's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to find your father\Nin Ryoji's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I recognized my father in Ryoji back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I ran away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid.\NIt was like my father and I were...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is,\NI ran away because I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were moments of utter bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they're right.\N"You never have a reason to fall in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but you always have a reason\Nto fall {\i1}out{\i0} of love."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kind, Ryoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that kindness... I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Make me filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to hurt yourself just because\Nyou hate who you are at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just using momentary punishment\Nto distract yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that I should\Ntake care of myself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Men are all like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They get lost in their work,\Nin their own little worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what Father did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always running away\Nfrom a harsh reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Harsh reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be. Just look at me.\NCould anybody blame him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Ms. Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't live with myself sometimes!\NI hate myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How indecent. That's filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How appalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so smutty! So absolutely gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what an adult relationship\Nis like?! I'm gonna puke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your promotion,\NMajor Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The me that's respected is a character\Nthat I play to try to earn respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}real{\i0} you is always crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,AM I HAPPY?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,AM I HAPPY?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,AM I HAPPY?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not! This isn't happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT IS HAPPINESS?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the real me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just try to convince myself that it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go through life\Nunless we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We get scared if we're not with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We get anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone isn't sleeping next to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared of sleeping alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So sleeping by yourself\Nmakes you feel lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stand the hole in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you don't care who it's with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you just want to experience\Nsimple pleasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to soothe your suffering heart\Nwith those momentary escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just using men\Nas a means to that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! You're wrong! You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT COULD SHE BE WISHING FOR?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my heart inside your heart, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the same, it's also my heart\Ninside your heart, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,THE CASE OF ASUKA LANGLEY SORYU\N(PART 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, what do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need Mommy or Daddy.\NI'll live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm still crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly don't know\Nhow to deal with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like a doctor\Nto sound so unsure of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor is also a human being.\NAs I've told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's hard to believe that a woman\Nlike you could be rattled by a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's strangely mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So tightly wound\Nand absolutely unapproachable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She scares me sometimes.\NHave you ever sensed that about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.\NAnyway, you're Asuka's mother now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I became your wife\Nbefore I became her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-It was at the same time.\N-Yes, in terms of societal roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But while you can never\Nstop being her father,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stop being her mother\Nwhenever I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Mommy! Don't stop being my Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a good girl that you'll love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't stop being my Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So please look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Mommy! Please don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy hates Mommy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't need me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he never loved me in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He never really needed me\Nat all, I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So die with Mommy, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Daddy doesn't want us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a nuisance? Am I unwanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Die with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not your doll, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think for myself and live for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found her,\NMom was hanging from the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She had such a happy look on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hated that look on her face so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die. I don't want\Nto fade away and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want boys, either!\NAnd I don't want Dad or Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will be with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT DOES SHE WISH FOR?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll live for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate it! It's hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cast me aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is {\i0}this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What your father was working on.\NThe Human Instrumentality Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's what this is?\N-Part of it, looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is something\Nwe never really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What you experience\Nat any given time are mere facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own set of facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And memory of those facts\Ngradually become your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Some truths change\Nand transform over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a fact?\NThis is how everything turns out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of facts. This is just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the outcome you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wished for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. For destruction.\NA world where no one is saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's a world where nobody\Nsaved {\i1}me!{\i0} That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Destruction. Death.\NA return to nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,These are things you wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The world around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own world, one that exists alongside\Ntime and space and other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A world where you yourself choose\Nhow to interpret and accept things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's a world made up of\Nonly what was given to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT IS REALITY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A world of your own\Nthat you have no control over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean a world where everything\Nis decided for me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not. It's a world\Nwhere {\i1}you{\i0} make the decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a world where your heart\Ndecides how things will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT IS REALITY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The will to go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart that wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are things that\Nyou yourself wished for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This darkness and this strange world...\NYou're saying that I wished for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You wished for a closed-off world\Nthat's comfortable for you and only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect your fragile heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect your pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the natural outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,People can't live in a closed-off realm.\NIn a world all their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But you wished for the world, for\Nthe world around you, to be closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Driving away everything you dislike,\Nyou wished for a lonely world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own heart did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It culminated in this tiny world\Nof peace of mind for you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The shape it's taken here\Nis one possible ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of the world\Nthat you yourself brought about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,AND SO, THE QUEST FOR INSTRUMENTALITY
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,CONTINUES
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Endings. They can always{\i0}\N{\i1}be found after a beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will our wishes lead to our destruction?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is our hope death itself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final episode, "The Beast That{\i0}\N{\i1}Shouted 'I' at the Heart of the World".{\i0}
